**Empty state (no results):**
```json
{ "success": true, "data": [] }
```

---

## Security Rules Summary

| Rule | Enforcement |
|---|---|
| Deleted salons | `s.deleted_at IS NULL` — hardcoded, always applied |
| Inactive salons | `s.is_active = 1` AND `s.status = 'active'` — hardcoded |
| Private salons | `s.is_marketplace_enabled = 1` — hardcoded |
| No private data | Explicit `SELECT` columns only — no `SELECT *` |

All four safety gates sit in the **base SQL string** before any user-provided params are appended. They cannot be bypassed by crafting query strings.
